short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple extension which detects query strings in the ChatGPT URL and automatically enters them into the search box

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is a simple Chrome extension which loads a bit of Javascript to the ChatGPT website to detect if the "q" parameter was set, and if so, enters it into the chat bar.
